CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 1, 1956, pg. A13, reads: "Jackson - Elston Ritual - Mr. and Mrs. Oliver A. Elston greeted friends during the reception at the home of the bride's aunt, Mrs. Susie Burrell, in Homestead. The bride is the former Beatrice Jackson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Groom Oliver A. Elston, and bride Beatrice Jackson Elston wearing strapless gown with beaded bust and pearl choker, cutting four tiered cake inscribed "Beatrice and Oliver Elston", in Burrell home, Homestead
